52.7	Katsuhiro_Otomo	Katsuhiro Otomo	Katsuhiro Otomo ÅŒtomo Katsuhiro, born April 14, 1954) is a Japanese comic book creator, screenwriter and film director. He is best known as the creator of the manga Akira and its animated film adaptation. Otomo has also directed several live-action films, such as the 2006 feature film adaptation of the manga Mushishi.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Katsuhiro-otomo.jpg/230px-Katsuhiro-otomo.jpg
